long.am,ar,bg,bn,el,en,en_AU,et,fa,fil,gu,he,:
Best volume booster Chrome extension, increase sound volume video and music in Chrome quickly and easily. With this volume booster you can increaseany sound volume videos from thousands of websites.

It's also an tab volume controller. It can control the volume level of each tab separately. All volume settings for each tab will be saved automatically until you close it.

It can increase volume videos on any website.
It can increase volume music on any website.
It allows you to increase the volume live show you love! You can control the volume Live broadcasts in your browser now with this volume booster! 

You can control the volume sound using slider. You can control the volume sound using hotkeys . You can reset the volume settings played media from the extension pop-up menu. 

You do not need to register an account to use this volume booster. You can control volume sound any video or audio without register. This volume booster is for free to use. 

Use this professional volume booster for Chrome browser to get louder video and music from websites you like.

It's easy to use. Add this volume booster extension to Chrome browser in one minute. Click on the icon of this extension on the target website, you will begin to control volume sound in no time. It's easy, safe and free. You will boost volume sound video and music fast and free. Try it. You will like this extension.

Please note: Be mindful of speaker safety using volume control. Excessive volume increases can harm your speakers. Carefully manage the audio levels to avoid damaging your device's sound system.

Add this volume booster to your website browser and it works at once. It can accompany you when you are surfing on the internet and you will not be failed listen media with bad sound from now on. Just one click helps you to keep the sound level you want. It's easy and it saves your time and energy!

Note:
Volume Booster cooperates with Natutti LTD

By installing our extension you agree to our internal Privacy Policy and also automatically agree to the Privacy Policy and Terms of Use of the Natutti platform https://natutti.net/privacy-policy.html and https://natutti.net/terms-of-use.html
